==制作==
2013年5月在加州[[洛杉矶|洛杉矶]]和[[帕萨迪纳_(加利福尼亚州)|帕萨迪纳]]开拍<ref>{{cite news|title=Paul Thomas Anderson’s ‘Inherent Vice’ filming in Pasadena, CA today|url=http://www.onlocationvacations.com/2013/06/14/paul-thomas-andersons-inherent-vice-filming-in-pasadena-ca-today/|accessdate=June 26, 2013|newspaper=onlocationvacations.com|date=June 14, 2013|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131203020613/http://www.onlocationvacations.com/2013/06/14/paul-thomas-andersons-inherent-vice-filming-in-pasadena-ca-today/|archive-date=2013-12-03|dead-url=no}}</ref>，同年8月杀青。

英国音乐人[[强尼·格林伍德|强尼·格林伍德]]为影片配乐，音乐在伦敦的[[皇家爱乐乐团|皇家爱乐乐团]]进行录制<ref>{{cite news|title=Jonny Greenwood Scoring Paul Thomas Anderson’s ‘Inherent Vice’|url=http://filmmusicreporter.com/2014/02/06/jonny-greenwood-scoring-paul-thomas-andersons-inherent-vice/|accessdate=7 February 2014|newspaper=filmmusicreporter.com|date=6 February 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140306190824/http://filmmusicreporter.com/2014/02/06/jonny-greenwood-scoring-paul-thomas-andersons-inherent-vice/|archive-date=2014-03-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 评价 ==
根据189个专业影评[[烂番茄|烂番茄]]新鲜度为72%，[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上43篇影评得分81，取得普遍好评。一些影评人将本片列入[[邪典电影|邪典电影]]之中，Josh Brolin 和 Katherine Waterston 的演出获得广大肯定，不过一些人对复杂剧情感到不满。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/movies/moviesnow/la-et-mn-nyff-inherent-vice-paul-thomas-anderson-movie-pynchon-20141005-story.html|title=NYFF 2014: 'Inherent Vice' and the contemporary cult hit|last=Zeitchik|first=Steven|newspaper=[[The_Los_Angeles_Times|LA Times]]|date=October 5, 2014|accessdate=October 7, 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150109165637/http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/movies/moviesnow/la-et-mn-nyff-inherent-vice-paul-thomas-anderson-movie-pynchon-20141005-story.html|archive-date=2015-01-09|dead-url=no}}</ref>

